MENU FILE HEADER (Don't delete)
MENU FILE NAME: $popcontrib/x/xved/doit_menus/move_menu
WARNING: the following move commands will
not work with menu files. In menus move the
cursor with the mouse, or with keypad keys.

Move to top of file                         !!      vedtopfile
Move to end of file                         !!      vedendfile

Move to top of procedure                    !!      veddo(%'\\@adefine '%)
Move to end of procedure                    !!      veddo(%'/@aenddefine'%)

Screen left                                 !!      vedscreenleft
Screen right                                !!      vedscreenright
Screen up                                   !!      vedscreenup
Screen down                                 !!      vedscreendown
Text left                                   !!      vedtextleft
Text right                                  !!      vedtextright

Move up "lots"                              !!      RETURNAFTER vedcharuplots
Move down "lots"                            !!      RETURNAFTER vedchardownlots
Move left "lots"                            !!      RETURNAFTER vedcharleftlots
Move right "lots"                           !!      RETURNAFTER vedcharrightlots

Move word right                             !!      RETURNAFTER vedwordright
Move word left                              !!      RETURNAFTER vedwordleft

Move up a line                              !!      RETURNAFTER vedcharup
Move down a line                            !!      RETURNAFTER vedchardown
Scroll menu      ----->                     !!      'menu scroll'
Menu menu        ----->                     !!      'menu menu'
